1-m%E1%BA%A1t-tam-tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-ReTo32Ylx4hiUvEOYxfkfA">Đề mạt tam tuyệt cú kỳ 2 - 題帕三絕句其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/H%C3%A0n-than-%C4%91%C3%A3i-phi%E1%BA%BFm-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-vu0tjwSQvoDVXz1RmWNmpg">Hàn than đãi phiếm kỳ 2 - 寒灘待泛其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%ADn/L%C3%A2m-giang-ti%C3%AAn/poem-Tam6g6B6sk3tK9d3Qvy-TA">Lâm giang tiên - 臨江仙</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%ADn/author-eBGdtm3O4c2NQ7sIhikeXg">Dương Thận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Ph%E1%BA%A3n-chi%C3%AAu-h%E1%BB%93n/poem-e9ahXuxrGyDkU5kL3GOwjQ">Phản chiêu hồn - 反招魂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/T%E1%BB%91ng-nh%C3%A2n-t%C3%B2ng-qu%C3%A2n/poem-PdiD7gNwD-aguIXC-Mkuqw">Tống nhân tòng quân - 送人從軍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br></div>	</div>
